    "This dataset was selected as it is widely used for robot indoor navigation [41].",
    "In particular, four houses with an average size of 22 × 25 m from MP3D were imported into Isaac Sim, Fig. 6.",
    "In each house, we randomly generated 20 pairs of start and goal positions and conducted 500 trials for each of the six robot embodiments used in Section VI.A. 1) Results: Fig.",
    "7 presents the SR and SPL for all configurations.",
    "Overall, X-Nav's SR and SPL increased with the number of random embodiments used for training."
